  "prompt": "What is the best site to download Hindi music for free?",
  "response": "When it comes to downloading Hindi music for free, it's important to prioritize legal and ethical sources to support artists and the music industry. Here are some legitimate options where you can access Hindi music legally:\n\n### 1. **YouTube**\n   - You can listen to Hindi music on YouTube legally, and some songs can be downloaded for offline listening using YouTube Premium.\n   - There are also official YouTube channels for music labels like T-Series, Zee Music Company, and Sony Music India.\n\n### 2. **Gaana**\n   - Gaana offers a vast library of Hindi songs. While it has a premium subscription, you can still listen to music for free with ads.\n\n### 3. **JioSaavn**\n   - JioSaavn provides a wide range of Hindi music. The free version includes ads, but you can access a lot of content legally.\n\n### 4. **Wynk Music**\n   - Wynk by Airtel offers free streaming of Hindi songs with ads. You can download songs for offline listening if you subscribe to their premium plan.\n\n### 5. **Spotify**\n   - Spotify has a huge collection of Hindi music. The free tier allows ad-supported streaming, and you can download songs offline with a premium subscription.\n\n### 6. **SoundCloud**\n   - Many independent artists upload their Hindi songs on SoundCloud, and some tracks are available for free download.\n\n### 7. **Internet Archive**\n   - The Internet Archive is a non-profit digital library that offers some older Hindi songs and albums for free and legal download.\n\n### 8. **FreeMusicArchive**\n   - This site offers a variety of music, including some Hindi tracks, that are free to download and use legally.\n\n### Important Note:\nAvoid illegal or pirated websites, as they violate copyright laws and harm the artists and creators. Always choose legal platforms to support the music industry and enjoy high-quality, safe downloads.",
